= GUI

- notes: notes about a contact, text that gets stored in the state file
- suggest: suggest contact
  - create new page
  - two drop downs, and a text field + generate button (existing code)
  - send a message to each recipient with the secret shared key
  - also send the user's public id via message (to help verify)
  - filter the drop-downs to only include non-pending contacts

